adGenAosIfPerfHistoryMib.description: This MIB module defines high capacity performance statistics for interfaces within an AOS product. Copyright (C) ADTRAN, Inc. (2013).

adIfPhCurTable.name: adIfPhCurTable
adIfPhCurTable.description: This table contains current performance history information that has been recorded since the last 15 minute interval ended and from when the last 1 day interval ended. This table is indexed by by ifIndex which SHOULD be maintained in a persistent manner.

adIfPhCurEntry.name: adIfPhCurEntry
adIfPhCurEntry.description: This specifies the information contained in one entry of the adIfPerfHistoryCurTable. It is indexed by an interface's IfIndex.
